OL,3,CThe thorn in Labour's side: Will
OL,4,CStarmer scrap the two-child benefit
OL,5,Ccap?
OL,7,FThe two-child benefit cap is fast
OL,8,Fbecoming a thorn in Labour's side.
OL,10,FThe cap, which restricts the ability
OL,11,Fof some families to claim benefits for
OL,12,Ftheir first two children, came into
OL,13,Feffect in April 2017.
