OL,7,FAt the time, the then-Conservative
OL,8,Fgovernment insisted the policy would
OL,9,Fmake the welfare system more
OL,10,Faffordable and ensure those on
OL,11,Fbenefits faced the "same financial
OL,12,Fchoices about having children as those
OL,13,Fsupporting themselves solely through
OL,14,Fwork".
