OL,5,Ccap?
OL,7,FFresh data published on Thursday has
OL,8,Frevealed that 1.6 million children now
OL,9,Flive in households impacted by the
OL,10,Fpolicy, compared to 1.5 million to
OL,11,FApril 2023.
OL,13,FITV News understands that some MPs are
OL,14,Fdiscussing how to force a vote or
OL,15,Fdebate on the issue, ahead of the
OL,16,FKing's Speech, which will outline
OL,17,FStarmer's parliamentary agenda.
