OL,3,CThe thorn in Labour's side: Will
OL,4,CStarmer scrap the two-child benefit
OL,5,Ccap?
OL,7,FLabour's Kim Johnson has long
OL,8,Fcampaigned for the policy to be
OL,9,Fscrapped and is planning on laying an
OL,10,Famendment to Speech, due to take place
OL,11,Fnext week.
OL,13,F"The families I represent just cannot
OL,14,Fwait any longer," she told ITV News.
OL,16,F"Labour has a huge task to undo 14
OL,17,Fyears of Tory decay and will have to
OL,18,Fmake difficult decisions about what to
OL,19,Fprioritise.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
