OL,3,CThe thorn in Labour's side: Will
OL,4,CStarmer scrap the two-child benefit
OL,5,Ccap?
OL,7,F"But I would like to see lifting the
OL,8,Ftwo child benefits cap a priority for
OL,9,Fthe new government as the most cost
OL,10,Feffective and most impactful way to
OL,11,Fimmediately alleviate child poverty in
OL,12,Fcommunities like mine across the
OL,13,Fcountry," she said.
OL,15,FAnother Labour MP told ITV News that
OL,16,Fthe "strength of opinion" on this
OL,17,Fissue was growing, and in recent days
OL,18,Fother Labour parliamentarians such as
OL,19,FIan Byrne and Andy McDonald have also
OL,20,Fvocalised support for scrapping the
OL,21,Fpolicy on social media.
