OL,7,FFormer Shadow Chancellor John
OL,8,FMcDonnell told the Mirror newspaper
OL,9,Fthat he was also considering tabling
OL,10,Famendments to the King's Speech and
OL,11,Fthe upcoming Autumn Budget.
OL,13,F"It's inevitable the Government are
OL,14,Fgoing to have to concede on this and
OL,15,Fthey might as well just announce it
OL,16,Fbefore the King's Speech so we don't
OL,17,Fneed to have any argument about this,"
OL,18,Fhe said.
