OL,7,F"We will work to give every child the
OL,8,Fbest start in life by delivering our
OL,9,Fmanifesto commitment to implement an
OL,10,Fambitious strategy to reduce child
OL,11,Fpoverty.
OL,13,F"I will hold critical meetings with
OL,14,Fcharities and experts next week to get
OL,15,Fthis urgent work under way," she said.
OL,17,FMany Labour MPs in particular hope
OL,18,Fthat this punchy rhetoric will
OL,19,Feventually be accompanied with a
OL,20,Fchange of position from the government.
